@startuml
actor "Shipping Agent Representative" as Agent
boundary "VVN Management API" as System

== Update VVN Fields ==
Agent -> System : PUT /api/vvn/{id}\nBody: UpdateVesselVisitNotificationDto\n(ETA, ETD, Volume, Docks, Documents, etc.)
System --> Agent : 200 OK\nBody: VesselVisitNotificationDto (updated)\nOR 400 Bad Request

== Withdraw VVN ==
Agent -> System : PUT /api/vvn/{id}/withdraw
System --> Agent : 200 OK\nStatus: Withdrawn

== Submit for Approval ==
Agent -> System : PUT /api/vvn/{id}/submit
System --> Agent : 200 OK\nStatus: Submitted
@enduml